---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<!-- Astro -->
<Layout
  title="Telehealth Counseling & Medication Services Across Idaho | MWRS"
  description="Online counseling and psychiatric medication management for clients anywhere in Idaho. MWRS provides secure telehealth visits for individuals, teens, couples, and families statewide."
>
  <main class="subpage">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="subpage-hero">
      <div class="subpage-hero-inner">
        <h1>Telehealth Services</h1>
        <p>
          MWRS offers secure telehealth counseling and medication management for
          clients across Idaho. Sessions take place through a HIPAA-compliant
          video platform, giving you flexible access to care from home, work, or
          anywhere you can find a quiet, private space.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact-us" class="subpage-btn"> Start telehealth care </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Body -->
    <section class="subpage-section">
      <div class="subpage-inner">
        <h2>Convenient and flexible</h2>
        <p>
          Telehealth works well for many clients, including those with long
          commutes, tight schedules, caregiving responsibilities, or limited
          access to in-person services. All you need is a smartphone, tablet, or
          computer with internet access.
        </p>

        <h2>Who can use telehealth</h2>
        <p>
          We provide telehealth counseling and medication management to adults
          and teens located anywhere in Idaho. Some clients choose telehealth
          exclusively; others use a mix of in-person and video sessions based on
          the season of life they’re in.
        </p>

        <h2>What telehealth sessions are like</h2>
        <p>
          Telehealth appointments function much like in-person visits. You and
          your provider meet face-to-face on video, discuss what’s been going
          on, and work toward the goals you’ve set together. If you’re seeking
          medication care, your provider can evaluate symptoms, adjust treatment
          plans, and coordinate labs when needed.
        </p>

        <h3>Telehealth is often a good fit for:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Busy parents or caregivers</li>
          <li>Clients who live outside city centers</li>
          <li>College students or remote workers</li>
          <li>People with mobility challenges or chronic illness</li>
          <li>Anyone who feels more comfortable at home</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Technology requirements</h2>
        <p>Telehealth sessions require:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>A stable internet connection</li>
          <li>A device with a camera and microphone</li>
          <li>A private, confidential space for the duration of the session</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          Before your first appointment, our team will send simple instructions
          to join your session and test your device if needed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <section class="subpage-section subpage-cta">
      <div class="subpage-inner">
        <h2>Ready to begin?</h2>
        <p>
          Telehealth makes it easier to start care wherever you’re located in
          Idaho. Share a few details on our intake form and we’ll match you with
          the right counselor or prescriber.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact-us" class="subpage-btn"> Start telehealth care </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    .subpage {
      background: #f9fafb;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* Hero */
    .subpage-hero {
      padding: 10rem 1.5rem 3rem;
      background-color: #fbfbf9; /* keep your soft white */
      background-image: url("/images/paper-texture.png");
      background-repeat: repeat; /* tile it */
      background-size: 420px 420px; /* tweak smaller/larger as you like */
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    .subpage-hero-inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .subpage-hero h1 {
      font-family: "Belleza", sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .subpage-hero p {
      margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    /* Shared sections */
    .subpage-section {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem 3.2rem;
      background: #e5e9f3;
      background-image: url("/images/paper-texture.png");
      background-repeat: repeat; /* tile it */
      background-size: 420px 420px; /* tweak smaller/larger as you like */
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    .subpage-cta {
      background: #fbfbf9;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
    }

    .subpage-inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .subpage-section h2 {
      font-family: "Belleza", sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .subpage-section h3 {
      margin: 1.1rem 0 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .subpage-section p {
      margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
      font-size: 0.96rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .subpage-section ul {
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      padding-left: 1.1rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .subpage-section li + li {
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
    }

    .subpage-cta p {
      max-width: 620px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    /* Button */
    .subpage-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.85rem 1.9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #0f172a;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #0f172a;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      transition:
        background 0.15s ease,
        color 0.15s ease,
        box-shadow 0.15s ease,
        transform 0.15s ease;
    }

    .subpage-btn:hover {
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #ffffff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.2);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
